title: League of Legends OCE Discord Server 2019

embed.description: Check out the League Of Legends OCE community on Discord - hang out with 72 other members and enjoy free voice and text chat.

body:
https://discord.gg/WpYBH96

Welcome to the new OCE League of Legends Discord Server. Come chat, play and interact with fellow OCE players that share your interest in League of Legends. Remember to be friendly and have a great time. The server is still being set up so your patience is greatly appreciated.

replies.body: What happened to the other one? I just noticed that it's gone!
i joined and got banned for no reason
